episodes.title: 21. Monica Misiura: A complex trauma survivor breaking the silence of 21 years of abuse - Part One
episodes.description: Welcome to another episode of the Alchemical VOICES podcast! Today's episode is Part One of a two-part series; I am joined by Monica Misiura, a complex trauma survivor breaking the silence of 21 years of abuse. Monica is an adventurous, highly intelligent, intuitive woman dedicated to helping others through massage and bodywork through the lens of a trauma-informed practitioner. Topics this episode touches on: 🎙️Domestic violence 🎙️Narcisstic abuse 🎙️Child sexual abuse (CSA) 🎙️Self-harm⠀⠀⠀ 🎙️Monica's time at Synanon Monica's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/monica.massage.therapy/ ⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ Did you learn something new?
